{"tid":2308674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師建議澳洲1招抗中：保證跳起來","createTime":"2020-12-02T05:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T14:20:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":650,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"b591e122b6110c14a3558d468bcc8ea830bd90ef","tid":2308674,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:14:51.000Z","msg":"澳洲駐阿富汗軍人殺害平民及俘虜，中國外交部發言人趙立堅見獵心喜，竟在推特PO出中國網友的諷刺畫作進行嘲諷，引發兩國隔空交火，有澳媒更以頭版刊登1989年六四天安門事件「坦克人」的照片予以回擊。不過律師林智群提供一招更狠的辦法，保證中國氣到跳起來，那就是「總理搭飛機來台灣一趟」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2NsZi5lV3lzhAzfaQPohTw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Ny45NTE4MDcyMjg5MTU2/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Gi02yHBeFh8mHS.bec_tFQ--~B/aD0zMDU7dz00OTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/setn.com.tw/c2d5817fa3f91e4becbe527b5f6dfda4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2NsZi5lV3lzhAzfaQPohTw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Ny45NTE4MDcyMjg5MTU2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGi02yHBeFh8mHS.bec_tFQ--~B%2FaD0zMDU7dz00OTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fc2d5817fa3f91e4becbe527b5f6dfda4&h=6d56f655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林智群認為澳洲若讓莫里森訪台就能狠踩中國痛腳。（圖／翻攝自Scott Morrison推特）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/律師建議澳洲1動作抗中-保證跳起來-033037175.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B21%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD-%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E8%B7%B3%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86-033037175.html&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2aVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=091b2c86\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/律師建議澳洲1動作抗中-保證跳起來-033037175.html</a>"},{"pid":"2153aceca6b726d332ab9944b9ad82202a713477","tid":2308674,"uid":51271,"like":212,"dislike":2,"score":210,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"咁又係，我包趙立堅唔敢出聲"},{"pid":"0f860171ef51c8632ceb643d7fa4de056b0443ef","tid":2308674,"uid":3